oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Buzzfest 6 featuring Staind, 3 Days Grace, Breaking Benjamin, Cowboy Mouth, Evans Blue, Soil, Blackstone Cherry, Luna Halo, and Ligion at Starwood Amphitheatre on August 26. Poster features woodcuts of stars, and the suits of a deck of cards (spade, diamond, club, and heart.
